We have still not sufficiently stopped the spread of COVID-19. Not hammered down, and dancing on the edge of a cliff. Rt simply going up and down 1 but never sufficiently far below.

New variants and government overexcited to loosen restrictions.

The end of the pandemic is far from sight.
